snippet.title: Anvil Empires - Announcement Trailer | Medieval War MMO
snippet.description:
Anvil is a massively multiplayer game where thousands of players work together to build empires, wage war, and conquer in a persistent online world.

Wishlist on Steam today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1373910

Follow the game to learn more:
Website: http://www.anvilempires.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/siegecamp
Discord: https://discord.gg/pEZs9MuDka
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/anvilempires

Music by Rom Di Prisco
